  <scopecontent id="aspace_df595be8cdc3665c37747de523f537ce">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>The collection contains primarily correspondence files as well as course work materials that date from his undergraduate days at the University of Massachusetts, which awarded him a B. S. in 1948. Watson received his M. S. from Rutgers University in 1950.</p><p> Also, subject files including plum varies.</p>  </scopecontent>
